.TH vdf_get_string_recursive 3

.SH NAME
vdf_get_string_recursive

.SH LIBRARY
Valve Data Format Parser Library (libvdfc)

.SH SYNOPSIS
#include <vdfc/vdf.h>

const char *vdf_get_string_recursive(const VDFNode *object, const char *key, const char *fallback);

.SH DESCRIPTION
Look up a `key` anywhere in the subtree at `object`, depth-first, and return its string value.

If no matching string node is found anywhere in the subtree, return `fallback`.

.SH RETURN VALUE
Returns the child's string value, or `fallback`.

.SH ERRORS
None.

